high_descs: Turn to the left, move towards the fridge, turn left and face the tomato on the table.
Pick up the tomato on the table.
Turn around and bring the tomato to the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Take the heated tomato from the microwave, turn around, bring the heated tomato back to the table with the coffee machine.
Put the heated tomato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the table in front of the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the table
Grab the tomato on the table
Turn right, walk to the microwave
Put the tomato in the microwave, turn on the microwave, open the microwave, take the tomato out
Turn around, walk to the white table
Put the tomato back on the table
anns.task_desc: Heat the tomato from the table in the microwave, put it back on the table

high_descs: Move to stand at the end of the white table closest to the fridge, facing the coffee maker on the table.
Pick up the tomato from the table.
Turn around and carry the tomato to the microwave, which is above the sinks.
Place the tomato inside the microwave, turn it on, and then remove, once heated.
Turn around and carry the tomato back to the white table.
Place the tomato on the table in front of the sharp knife and to the right of the paper towels.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated tomato on the white table.
